methods.receiveErr:
Registers interest in System.err.

:return: (java.util.Optional<java.io.OutputStream>) if present, represents interest in receiving System.err calls.
methods.receiveOut:
Registers interest in System.out.

:return: (java.util.Optional<java.io.OutputStream>) if present, represents interest in receiving System.out calls.

text:
Allows classes to register interest in receiving application level calls to System.out and
 System.err.
